                            <comment id="12973052" author="kristwaa" created="Sun, 19 Dec 2010 23:00:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attaching patch 1a, which addresses the issue much in the same way as getProviders (creates a copy of the list).&lt;/p&gt;

