Patch ready for review.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12973056" author="kristwaa" created="Sun, 19 Dec 2010 23:08:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Added link to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4928&quot; title=&quot;Deadlock-prone synchronization in BasicDependencyManager&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-4928&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-4928&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, which introduced this bug (I assume it is new, although the failing test is also rather new and is only failing intermittently).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12973141" author="knutanders" created="Mon, 20 Dec 2010 09:09:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Moving the copying of the list into the synchronized block looks like a correct fix to me. +1 to commit.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
